{"type": "article", "id": 24076, "title": "带抽屉的椭圆形咖啡桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-18T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144106EjUAcZ7YNHClXbVp.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个椭圆形的桌子是一张咖啡桌，桌面的一头是绿色的，用来做咖啡托盘。向内划开后则能发现一个圆形的粉色储物柜，可以放一些毛线等小的物品。在原本简单普通的咖啡桌里隐藏了一些小的心思。桌面和桌腿都非常圆润，让这张桌子显得轻盈小巧。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144103vf6hktCmRVxlTZcF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144104GqU5ub1dgP3KVMQj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144104iO6TKwU47gceZVo2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144105jEmWBv4ehDfzO16k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}